Package: bibloCNKI
Title: Bibliometric Analysis Toolkit for CNKI-style Literature Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides tools for analyzing bibliometric data from CNKI (China National Knowledge Infrastructure) 
    formatted datasets. Contains functions for cumulative publication trend visualization, geographic heatmapping 
    of research institutions, keyword temporal analysis with dumbbell plots, and comprehensive bibliometric 
    analytics. Specializes in handling Chinese academic data formats and character encodings.
